thread.title: Norman A Caetano
thread.title_full: WholeLatteLove.com reviewed by Norman A Caetano

author: Norman A Caetano
title: Norman A Caetano
text: Whole Latte provided my Silvia in 1994 and kept her going since. A great source for coffee machines, coffee machine cleaning supplies, and everything else that could be imagined for coffee machines. They have great library of video and information on espresso and espresso machines. Good prices and fast delivery. Whole Latte Love provides the love for coffee folks.
